	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Salve, mi omnium longe charissime et optime frater.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Rediit nudius tertius charissimus consobrinus <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p4082" cert="high">Zviccius</persName> multam mihi tuis verbis salutem dicens, pro qua vicissim plurimam tibi gratiam habeo.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quod de novis rebus ad te nunc scribam, nihil prorsus habeo.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Magna est omnium apud nos expectatio, quid de nobis <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18538" cert="high">Caesar</persName>, imo dominus ipse per <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18538" cert="high">Caesarem</persName> statuat.</s>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Orate pro nobis nostraque ecclesia, ut in ipso ad sui nominis gloriam adversus omnes inferorum portas conservetur.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Mitto a <persName ref="p6552" cert="high">Schönero</persName> nostro literas, sed ni fallor, iampridem datas, quandoquidem et illę, quas ad me dedit, calendis Ianuarii ab illo sunt scriptę.</s>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Miseret me valde miselli seniculi<note xml:id="fna" type="footnote" n="a"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p6552" cert="high">Hans Schöner</persName>.</note>, et tamen non video quicquam, quod ab <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l18" cert="high">Augustanis</placeName> commode sperare possit.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Soror illius <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p6555" cert="high">Sabina</persName> te officiosissime iubet salvere; misit ad te nescio quos orbiculos medicos; eos ubi accepero, quamprimum ut habeas curabo.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Sonst nichts, dann yetz kompt ain gschray, der landtvogt welle morn suntag mandata verkünden lassen, das man unß ausß dem <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l774" cert="high">Turgöw</placeName> ouch nichts herin lasse etc. was mehr darzuͦ gehört, daruff meine herren glych yetz uff <placeName ref="l159" cert="high">Frowenfeld</placeName> geschickt und sölichs an dem landtvogt erfaren lassen, ouch inn ze bitten, wa dem allso, das er doch damitt still ston welle, byß myne herren ir bottschafft an die von <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l587" cert="high">Zuͤrich</placeName> oder gemain <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l862" cert="high">aidgnossen</placeName> schicken mögind.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Unser bischoff ist in starcken, treffelichen practicen, soll selbs auff nechsten tag kommen.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ach gott, was will doch noch daruß werden.</s>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Bittend gott trulich fuͤr uns, das wir an im trüw, uffrecht und redlich belybind, es ganag zuͦ kopff oder napff, es gelte leben oder sterben.</s>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salutant te nostri.</s>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Salveat tua domus cum omnibus fratribus et amicis.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">3. Martii 1548.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName ref="p8055" cert="high">Ambrosius Blaurerus</persName>.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<note type="address">[Adresse:]</note>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Bullingero</persName> suo.</s>
					<s n="18" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName ref="l587" type="citizen_name" cert="high">Tiguri</placeName>.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
